hw3

类 FourOfAKindEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • hw3.FourOfAKindEvaluator

  • public class FourOfAKindEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
    Evaluator for a hand containing (at least) four cards of the same rank. The number of cards required is four. The name of this evaluator is "Four of a Kind".
